Rating: 4
This is an excellent, easy to prepare recipe. Great for summer menus. I substituted 2TBL olive oil and 4TBL mayonnaise for the canola oil, which tastes MUCH better if you're not counting fat grams. Also, added some finely diced red onion - very nice. The fresh dill makes the salad, so skip this one if you don't have fresh. Enjoy!

